 smoker**                                                                       
IUD**                  0.8     0.8      1.0       1.0       1.4      1.4        
Condom*                1.1     1.6      0.7       0.2       0.3      0.4        
Diaphragm/spermicide*  1.9     1.2      1.2       1.3       2.2      2.8        
