     Dyspepsia                                        2.2                0.5
     Mouth or Throat Dry                              1.7                0.5
     Constipation                                     1.5                0.8
     Dental Abnormalities                             1.5                0.3
     Increased Appetite                               1.1                0.8
Hematologic and Lymphatic Systems
     Leukopenia                                       1.1                0.5
Musculoskeletal System
     Myalgia                                          2.0                1.9
     Fracture                                         1.1                0.8
Nervous System
     Somnolence                                      19.3                8.7
     Dizziness                                       17.1                6.9
     Ataxia                                          12.5                5.6
     Nystagmus                                        8.3                4.0
     Tremor                                           6.8                3.2
     Nervousness                                      2.4                1.9
