<head>
   <title>Actaminophen - RxList Generic Information</title>
   <meta name="keywords" content="APAP, Abenol,  Acamol,  Acetalgin,  Acetamol,  Acetan, 
Acropirina,  Afebrin,  Alvedon,  Anaflon,  Analfen,  Analgiser,  Anapark, 
Arfen,  Asidon,  Benuron,  Calapol,  Calip,  Calpol,  Ceetamol,  Crocin, 
Custodia,  Datril,  Dirox,  Dolamin,  Doliprane,  Dolofen,  Dolomol, 
