Hydrochloride </font></p></center>

<center><p><font SIZE=+1>120 mg Every 12 Hours (twice recommended dose)
</font></p></center>

<center><p><font SIZE=+1>in Normal Volunteers (n=24)</font>
<br></p></center>

<table>
<tr>
