<p><a name="OVERDOSAGE"></a><b>OVERDOSAGE </b></p>

<p>There have been reported cases of overdosage with Gemfibrozil. In one
case a 7 year old child recovered after ingesting up to 9 grams of Gemfibrozil.
Symptomatic supportive measures should be taken should an overdose occur.
</p>

<p><a name="DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION"></a><b>DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION
</b></p>

<p>The recommended dose for adults is 1200 mg administered in two divided
doses 30 minutes before the morning and evening meal. </p>

<p>REFERENCES </p>

