                   (mean)   (mean)  (mean)  (mean)   (mean)   (median) (median) 
Lovastatin                                                                         
40 mg q.p.m.  47     -25     -32      +9      -38      -31       -37     -18    
80 mg q.p.m.  49     -30     -37     +11      -42      -36       -27     -17    
