2:1048-1049, 1980. </p>

<p>4. Katz RA, Jorgensen H, Nigra TP: Elevation of serum triglyceride levels
from oral isotretinoin in disorders of keratinization. Arch Dermatol 116:1369-1372,
1980. </p>

<p>5. Dicken CH, Connolly SM: Eruptive xanthomas associated with isotretinoin
